M|brand-guidelines|**Main Colors:**
M|brand-guidelines|- Dark: `#141413` - Primary text and dark backgrounds
M|brand-guidelines|- Light: `#faf9f5` - Light backgrounds and text on dark
M|brand-guidelines|- Mid Gray: `#b0aea5` - Secondary elements
M|brand-guidelines|- Light Gray: `#e8e6dc` - Subtle backgrounds
M|brand-guidelines|**Accent Colors:**
M|brand-guidelines|- Orange: `#d97757` - Primary accent
M|brand-guidelines|- Blue: `#6a9bcc` - Secondary accent
M|brand-guidelines|- Green: `#788c5d` - Tertiary accent
M|brand-guidelines|- **Headings**: Poppins (with Arial fallback)
M|brand-guidelines|- **Body Text**: Lora (with Georgia fallback)
M|brand-guidelines|- **Note**: Fonts should be pre-installed in your environment for best results
